---
import NousLogo from "@/assets/NousLogo.svg";

---
<!-- About Us Bento Grid Section -->
<section 
    class="mt-40 sm:mt-48 lg:mt-64 xl:mt-80 appear-subtle "
    aria-labelledby="about-section-heading"
>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4 sm:gap-6 ">
        
        
        <article class="md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-6 bg-gradient-to-br border border-outline from-primary-blue/20 to-outline/20 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-center">
                
                <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start items-center order-1 lg:order-1">
                    <img 
                        src={NousLogo.src} 
                        alt="Nous Technologies Logo" 
                        class="w-auto h-16 sm:h-20 lg:h-24" 
                        loading="lazy"
                    />   
                </div>
                
                
                <div class="lg:col-span-2 order-2 lg:order-2">
                    <h2 
                        id="about-section-heading"
                        class="font-archivo-black text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl mb-4 sm:mb-6 text-accent leading-tight"
                    >
                    Founded with a clear vision:
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-pretty text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                        To democratize technology consulting in Latin America—giving every company, from startups to large enterprises, access to independent guidance and production-ready execution in two tracks: AI automation and modern web development.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        
        <article class="md:col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br border border-outline from-primary-blue/20 to-outline/20 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6 ">
            <header class="mb-4 sm:mb-6">
                <h3 class="font-archivo-black text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl text-accent">
                    Purpose
                </h3>
            </header>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-pretty text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold text-outline">Turn real problems into momentum.</span> We remove busywork with automation or win customers with high-performing web—measured in hours saved, revenue gained, and happier users. Pragmatic, outcome-first, no hype.
            </p>
        </article>

        
        <article class="md:col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br border border-outline from-primary-blue/20 to-outline/20 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6">
            <header class="mb-4 sm:mb-6">
                <h3 class="font-archivo-black text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl text-accent">
                    Vision
                </h3>
            </header>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-pretty text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold text-outline">Latam, world-class by default.</span> By 2030, be the region’s most trusted partner for practical technology change—making AI automation and web excellence accessible to organizations of any size. World-class delivery without a Silicon Valley zip code.
            </p>
        </article>

        
        <article class="md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2 bg-gradient-to-br border border-outline from-primary-blue/20 to-outline/20 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6">
            <header class="mb-4 sm:mb-6">
                <h3 class="font-archivo-black text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl text-accent">
                    Mission
                </h3>
            </header>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-pretty text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold text-outline">Empower teams to work smarter and grow faster.</span> Founded in 2025 in Costa Rica, we provide clear advisory, short cycles, and solutions that run reliably in production—independent, vendor-neutral, and committed to outcomes you can measure.
            </p>
        </article>
        
    </div>
</section>